This paper is primarily focused on age estimation using computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models for this task, which is a popular area of research in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image processing and analysis, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM) and computer graphics (cs.CR).
